rows.label: qev090201_MSG0001
rows.name: Man, these missions blow chunks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0002
rows.name: You got any inside tips on somethin' with a bit more kick?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0003
rows.name:
This planet must have more to it than
pickin' flowers and collectin' junk.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_JNK0010
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: qev090201_SEL0011
rows.name:
Tell Yelv that you have seen things
that would blow his mind.

rows.label: qev090201_JNK0020
rows.name: Shrug

rows.label: qev090201_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Yelv that you've got nothing.

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0004
rows.name: I'm jealous, pard. You get all the fun![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0005
rows.name:
Who's a guy gotta bribe around here
to get a piece of that action?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0006
rows.name: Yeah, figures it wouldn't be that easy...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0007
rows.name:
Hey, I know! What say you and me
go sniff around the city for leads?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0008
rows.name: Maybe we'll catch wind of some juicy rumors.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0009
rows.name:
Sometimes ol' Joe Lunchbucket knows more
about this stuff than us BLADEs.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0010
rows.name:
Heh. When I was in the military back on Earth,
I used to get all my tips from locals.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0011
rows.name:
My buddy and me would even sneak off base
and moonlight as bouncers at seedy bars![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_JNK0030
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: qev090201_SEL0031
rows.name: Join in on Yelv's plan.

rows.label: qev090201_JNK0040
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: qev090201_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask about Yelv's army days.

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0012
rows.name: All right, pard, let's do this. The city's our oyster, baby![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0013
rows.name:
Got sent to the middle of the god-forsaken
desert right after enlistin'.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0014
rows.name:
Nothin' but sand and scorpions for miles,
so me and my buddy were always sneakin' off.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0015
rows.name:
We got in good with the boys in the nearest town—
had some real wild times.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0016
rows.name:
Casino security, flippin' military gear for cash...
Kinda crazy, now that I think about it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0017
rows.name:
But all that's down the crapper now,
so let's go find us some real action.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090201_MSG0018
rows.name:
We'll meet at the Sunshine Café once you
scrounge up a solid lead.[ST:wait ]
